---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Process">
  <section class="prose max-w-3xl">
    <h1>Process</h1>
    <p>How I approach narrative design - from discovery to implementation.</p>

    <h2>1) Discovery</h2>
    <p>Goals, audience, constraints, tone, references.</p>

    <h2>2) Structure</h2>
    <p>Beats, pacing, story pillars, branching logic (when relevant).</p>

    <h2>3) Writing</h2>
    <p>Dialogue, barks, item text, cutscenes, cinematics, VO notes.</p>

    <h2>4) Implementation</h2>
    <p>Engine tools, variables, conditions, flags, iteration with design.</p>

    <h2>5) Iteration</h2>
    <p>Playtests, feedback loops, polish passes.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

